subSubSection.paragraph: Distribution . Pacific Ocean: California; South China Sea; New Zealand ; Three Kings Island; southern Australia . In the present study this species was found in three samples from the surface to as deep as 1682– 1591 m and occurs from 20°S to 35°N and 83°– 126°W . Atlantic Ocean: 45°N– 45°S ; Mediterranean Sea; Gulf of Maine; Georges Bank; Bermuda ; New York–Azores; Madeira; Guinea Current. Indian Ocean: Red Sea; 5°N– 13°S .
